A simple and fun Hangman Game built in Python  
Try to guess the hidden word one letter at a time before you run out of lives!


##  Game Rules

1. A random word is selected from a predefined list.
2. The player sees blanks (`_ _ _ _`) for each letter in the word.
3. The player guesses one letter at a time.
   -  If the letter is in the word — it appears in the correct spot(s).
   -  If not — you lose one life.
4. You win if you guess the word before you lose all your lives!
